last_episode_to_air.name: The Club/Cory from Beyond
last_episode_to_air.overview: The Club: Donny has a date at the club with sweet Susie Selby, but is worried he might be inadequate — on the dance floor. Cory From Beyond: When Cory gets a cell phone for the first time, Donny begins receiving a series of mysterious text messages.

name: The Dress Up Gang
overview: In a surreal version of Los Angeles, Donny and Cory are roommates who look out for each other. Donny, a responsible adult with the temperament and outlook of a child, relies on guidance and life advice from Cory, the dad-like 30-something who has been crashing on his couch for quite some time.

episodes.name: Burger Buddies/New Day Look
episodes.overview: Burger Buddies: Donny gets in trouble when Cory finds out he is trying to go to McDonald's by himself. New Look Day: Cory hosts the annual New Look Day potluck, and Donny decides to go big this year.

episodes.name: Sigourney Weaver/Finding Frankie
episodes.overview: Sigourney Weaver: Donny feels confused when he discovers he has feelings for Sigourney Weaver. Finding Frankie: When Frankie has a bad mushroom trip and gets lost in the woods, his friends must find him and give him ecstasy before it's too late.

episodes.name: Summer Body Blues/The First Scuff Is the Deepest
episodes.overview: Summer Body Blues: Donny’s summer is in jeopardy when it’s discovered that his ripped body will make everyone at Raging Waters feel insecure. First Scuff is The Deepest: When Donny falls in love with a pair of all-white shoes, Cory worries he’ll have his heart broken.

episodes.name: Frankie's Fort/Wonko
episodes.overview: Frankies Fort: Frankie serves his house arrest at Donny's place, but tensions arise when Cory's taquito goes missing. Wonko: When Donny takes in a baby skunk, Christian will do whatever it takes to get his hands on the cute critter to impress his mistress.

episodes.name: Donny's Dinner Date/Toothpick
episodes.overview: Donny's Dinner Date: When Donny forgets to make a reservation for Valentine's Day, his friends come to the rescue. Toothpick: Donny's new habit has everyone concerned.

episodes.name: Dessert for Donny/The Handshake
episodes.overview: Dessert for Donny: Donny struggles to deal with peer pressure from the bad boy himself, Brent. The Handshake: Cory gets jealous when he discovers that Donny and Frankie have a secret handshake.

episodes.name: The Cockroach/The Bully
episodes.overview: The Cockroach: With everyone trapped inside Donny's house during a mojito party, Fox discovers something sinister lurking in the bathroom. The Bully: Cory teaches Donny how to defend himself from a blacked-out bully.

episodes.name: Big League/Cory's Truck
episodes.overview: Big League: After Christian "big leagues" Frankie at the mall and makes him feel like a buster, Donny vows to avenge his friend. Cory's Truck: When Donny discovers Cory owns a truck he's excited to find out where it's been parked all this time.

episodes.name: The Ding Dong Ditcher
episodes.overview: Cory and Donny become obsessed with catching the culprit terrorizing the courtyard.
